INSTALL HELP

(1) Open up key gen
(2) dbl click on "Gutterball2Setup.exe" to install
(3) After install go to "register by phone" to get "Product ID code" on the screen
(4) copy and paste that "Product ID Code" into the KeyGen "Product ID" line
(5) Click on the generate button
(6) Copy and paste the "Registration Code" into the "Registration Code" line on keygen
(7) Click on "generate"

this should work for you!!
This is a fun game!
TIP: Be careful with that mouse!!! 
:)
